high_descs: Turn around completely, turn right, walk to the head of the bed and turn left to face the bed.
Pick up the pillow that is closest to the headboard of the bed.
Walk to the opposite side of the bed where the nightstand sits.
Turn on the lamp that is on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Examine a pillow using the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward across the room to the pillows on the bed.
Pick up the pillow which is closest to the wall.
Turn left and walk past the bed, then turn right and walk across the room to the wall, then turn right and walk to the lamp on the night stand.
anns.task_desc: Examine a pillow by the light of a lamp on a night stand.

high_descs: Turn left and cross the room to the mirror on the other side of the room, then turn left and face the bed
Pick up the white pillow that is sitting on the bed closest to you
Turn left and walk to the end of the bed, take a right at the end of the bed, then another right to go around the bed. Walk to the night stand that is sitting to the left of the bed
Turn on the lamp that is sitting on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine a pillow under a light
